---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Home" description="Project UNAC is a black-canvas world archive and music portal by SHINHWI.">
  <section class="hero-type-band home-hero">
    <div class="container home-hero-frame">
      <div class="home-hero-copy">
        <p class="kicker">Official archive / Project UNAC</p>
        <h1 class="display-xl home-title">Project UNAC</h1>
        <div class="home-lead-group" aria-label="Project UNAC archive statement">
          <p class="lead home-lead">A black archive for a world told through story, sound, and image.</p>
          <p class="lead home-lead home-lead-ko">검은 문턱 너머의 신호와 장면을 소설, 음악, 이미지로 봉인해 두는 Project UNAC의 공식 기록.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-archive-rail" aria-label="Project UNAC archive index">
        <p class="archive-rail-marker">UNAC / INDEX 00</p>
        <div class="hero-index" aria-label="Archive identity">
          <p><span>Domain</span>World / Story / Sound / Image</p>
          <p><span>Archive mode</span>Black canvas / Official record / Restrained image</p>
        </div>
        <div class="button-row home-actions">
          <a class="button-primary" href="/project/">Read the statement</a>
          <a class="button-primary" href="/world/">Enter the archive</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section home-archive-section">
    <div class="container editorial-grid home-archive-grid">
      <div class="section-head home-section-head">
        <p class="kicker">Official record / 기록의 표면</p>
        <h2 class="display-lg">Black archive index</h2>
        <p class="body-copy">Project UNAC is arranged as a restrained record: a world portal, a serialized story surface, a sound archive, and a curated image register held together on a black canvas.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="archive-lines" aria-label="Archive sections">
        <a class="archive-line" href="/world/">
          <span class="archive-label">World record</span>
          <span>세계의 규칙, 인물, 세력, 연대기를 정리하는 공식 색인.</span>
        </a>
        <a class="archive-line" href="/story/">
          <span class="archive-label">Story ledger</span>
          <span>연재 소설과 장면의 흐름을 문장 중심으로 보존하는 기록.</span>
        </a>
        <a class="archive-line" href="/music/">
          <span class="archive-label">Sound register</span>
          <span>SHINHWI Originals와 Project UNAC OST를 나누어 보관하는 음악 장부.</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
